overview: They're cute, they're cuddly and, sometimes, babies are downright hilarious. Molly Shannon ("Saturday Night Live") hosts this collection of clips of babies just being babies, submitted by real-life families. All the milestones are covered here: birthdays, first steps, memorable messy meals and more, including some of the funniest moments on the road to toddlerhood.
title: Oh! Baby: You're on TV
